{"type":null,"faqId":44513,"title":"开启位置服务是否会耗费数据流量？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>通常来讲，开启位置服务后，手机在使用位置相关的应用时会加载地图等数据，会消耗数据流量。建议您在使用地图等软件时，先下载好离线地图并定期在WLAN环境下更新。这样手机在使用位置服务时可最大程度地节省流量消耗。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"14","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400820000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":7,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"位置服务,流量","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}